metadata.name: The Labyrinth
metadata.description:
Our Worst battle is between what we know and what we feel. 

Should I or should I not, the tiny voice in the back of your head always commanding you, 
warning you to be cautious.

Our deepest and darkest secrets hushed up inside us, 
constantly battling with us to let them out. 

This illustration is a take on the contemporary world. 

From the outside, all of us seem to get it but what goes through the heart and brain seems to be a different story.
